  "html": "<p><em>Hey ReFi Fam! ğŸ‘‹</em></p><p><em>Anna and Monty here with an invitation to <strong>join us on February 12th @ 4 PM UTC</strong> at the </em><a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><em>ReFi Local Nodes 2024 Kickoff call</em></a><em>, where we will introduce and provide updates on what's coming next for ReFi DAO, the DAO-ification process, the upcoming Local Node Incubator, and the first Collaboration Circles Cohort. This call is open to all the Local Node founders, ReFi enthusiasts and anyone else who wants to get involved with ReFi DAO! ğŸ‘‡</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Reserve Your Spot ğŸ“†</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi Local Nodes 2024 Kickoff - Beta Incubator and Collaboration Circles ğŸŒ± Â· Zoom Â· Luma</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Whatâ€™s next for ReFi DAO? Join this call for details on the ReFi DAO-ification process, the upcoming Local Node Beta Incubator, and Collaboration Circles Cohort 0? See you there! ğŸ‘€</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://lu.ma/apple-touch-icon.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">ReFi DAO Global</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://social-images.lu.ma/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=cover,dpr=1,quality=75,width=800,height=419/api/event-one?calendar_avatar=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Fcalendars%2F6y%2F35b392f0-8e71-48dc-9082-1069afb078a5&amp;calendar_name=ReFi%20DAO%20Global%20Events&amp;color0=%23232524&amp;color1=%233b3a43&amp;color2=%23748398&amp;color3=%23e8e8f3&amp;host_avatar=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Favatars%2Fhc%2Fb8a67eec-1837-44a1-958c-24f1e4729f16&amp;host_name=ReFi%20DAO%20Global&amp;img=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Fevent-covers%2Fxh%2F249f83d3-4f18-439f-ba04-9ca35b97cd50&amp;name=ReFi%20Local%20Nodes%202024%20Kickoff%20-%20Beta%20Incubator%20and%20Collaboration%20Circles%20%F0%9F%8C%B1\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><p><em>Here is a peek at what you can expect from this call. </em>â¬‡ï¸</p><hr><h2 id=\"refi-dao-ification-process-%F0%9F%A4%9D\">ReFi DAO-ification Process ğŸ¤</h2><p>After a fruitful <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/a-new-chapter-refi-dao-forum-4/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ReFi DAO Forum in December 2023</a>, where we aligned with the community on the objectives for 2024, the ReFi DAO-ification group has continued working on the Value Flow Compass, proposed and developed by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thetokenjedi?ref=blog.refidao.com\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Scott Morris</a>. By integrating collaborators, offerings, community, and accounts, the Canvas holds the potential to envision a comprehensive, equitable, and collaborative approach to ReFi DAO's future operations.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/02/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-4.48.23-pm-1.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2024/02/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-4.48.23-pm-1.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/02/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-4.48.23-pm-1.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/02/Screenshot-2024-02-05-at-6.12.17-pm.png\" width=\"1274\" height=\"1384\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2024/02/Screenshot-2024-02-05-at-6.12.17-pm.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2024/02/Screenshot-2024-02-05-at-6.12.17-pm.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/02/Screenshot-2024-02-05-at-6.12.17-pm.png 1274w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div><figcaption><p><i><em class=\"italic\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Compass developed by Scott Morris and originated from Zebras Unite cooperative patronage system</em></i></p></figcaption></figure><p>During the Kick-off call, we will share updates on the current state of the Value Flow Compass, how to get involved, and share a public draft of the new <strong>ReFi DAO Mission, Vision,</strong> <strong>Values </strong>statement for review. </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Reserve Your Spot ğŸ“†</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi Local Nodes 2024 Kickoff - Beta Incubator and Collaboration Circles ğŸŒ± Â· Zoom Â· Luma</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Whatâ€™s next for ReFi DAO? Join this call for details on the ReFi DAO-ification process, the upcoming Local Node Beta Incubator, and Collaboration Circles Cohort 0? See you there! ğŸ‘€</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://lu.ma/apple-touch-icon.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">ReFi DAO Global</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://social-images.lu.ma/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=cover,dpr=1,quality=75,width=800,height=419/api/event-one?calendar_avatar=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Fcalendars%2F6y%2F35b392f0-8e71-48dc-9082-1069afb078a5&amp;calendar_name=ReFi%20DAO%20Global%20Events&amp;color0=%23232524&amp;color1=%233b3a43&amp;color2=%23748398&amp;color3=%23e8e8f3&amp;host_avatar=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Favatars%2Fhc%2Fb8a67eec-1837-44a1-958c-24f1e4729f16&amp;host_name=ReFi%20DAO%20Global&amp;img=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Fevent-covers%2Fxh%2F249f83d3-4f18-439f-ba04-9ca35b97cd50&amp;name=ReFi%20Local%20Nodes%202024%20Kickoff%20-%20Beta%20Incubator%20and%20Collaboration%20Circles%20%F0%9F%8C%B1\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><hr><h2 id=\"refi-local-nodes-beta-incubator-%F0%9F%8C%8E%F0%9F%8C%8E%F0%9F%8C%8F\">ReFi Local Nodes Beta Incubator ğŸŒğŸŒğŸŒ</h2><p>2023 was marked by the passion and progress of ReFi Local Nodes across the globe. Check out <a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/refidao.eth/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Regenerative Journeys: ReFi Local Nodes 2023&nbsp;Roundup</a> to learn more! ğŸ‘‡</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-local-nodes-impact-2023/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Regenerative Journeys: ReFi Local Nodes 2023 Roundup âœ¨</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">In 2023, ReFi DAO Globalâ€™s network of ReFi Local Nodes spread to more than 20 countries. This article celebrates the incredible achievements of the Nodes, while they share their plans for the upcoming year. ğŸŒğŸŒ±ğŸ‰</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w256h256/2022/12/6319c4c1d0b248c635dc4002_ReFi-DAO.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">ReFi DAO</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Monty Merlin Bryant</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1200/2024/01/ZJOfsSw8YJG7exui15Jab.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><p>Now, after a successful <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-local-nodes-on-gitcoin/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Alpha Cohort</a>, we are pleased to invite both new and established Nodes to the Beta Cohort Incubator - a seven-week journey with a diverse range of leaders sharing insights and sessions tailored to guide you through the process of successfully establishing and maintaining a thriving Node. We have an exciting agenda to share with you ğŸ‘‡</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Join the Kick-Off</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi Local Nodes 2024 Kickoff - Beta Incubator and Collaboration Circles ğŸŒ± Â· Zoom Â· Luma</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Whatâ€™s next for ReFi DAO? Join this call for details on the ReFi DAO-ification process, the upcoming Local Node Beta Incubator, and Collaboration Circles Cohort 0? See you there! ğŸ‘€</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://lu.ma/apple-touch-icon.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">ReFi DAO Global</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://social-images.lu.ma/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=cover,dpr=1,quality=75,width=800,height=419/api/event-one?calendar_avatar=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Fcalendars%2F6y%2F35b392f0-8e71-48dc-9082-1069afb078a5&amp;calendar_name=ReFi%20DAO%20Global%20Events&amp;color0=%23232524&amp;color1=%233b3a43&amp;color2=%23748398&amp;color3=%23e8e8f3&amp;host_avatar=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Favatars%2Fhc%2Fb8a67eec-1837-44a1-958c-24f1e4729f16&amp;host_name=ReFi%20DAO%20Global&amp;img=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Fevent-covers%2Fxh%2F249f83d3-4f18-439f-ba04-9ca35b97cd50&amp;name=ReFi%20Local%20Nodes%202024%20Kickoff%20-%20Beta%20Incubator%20and%20Collaboration%20Circles%20%F0%9F%8C%B1\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><p>Thinking of starting a Local Node in your city? There is still time to apply. </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://tally.so/r/mK5VYM\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Apply Now</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe src=\"https://tally.so/embed/mK5VYM?hideTitle=1&amp;alignLeft=1\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" title=\"Tally Forms\" scrolling=\"auto\"></iframe><script>var d=document,w=\"https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js\",v=function(){\"undefined\"!=typeof Tally?Tally.loadEmbeds():d.querySelectorAll(\"iframe[data-tally-src]:not([src])\").forEach((function(e){e.src=e.dataset.tallySrc}))};if(\"undefined\"!=typeof Tally)v();else if(d.querySelector('script[src=\"'+w+'\"]')==null){var s=d.createElement(\"script\");s.src=w,s.onload=v,s.onerror=v,d.body.appendChild(s);}</script></figure><hr><h2 id=\"introducing-the-collaboration-circles-%F0%9F%8E%89\">Introducing The Collaboration Circles ğŸ‰</h2><p>With a diverse array of ReFi DAO global contributors and Local Nodes across the globe, how can we cultivate structures for meaningful, participatory, and productive collaboration across ReFi DAO? Following on from the Beta Incubator, we are excited to share a new program for ReFi CoordiNATION... </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/02/Collaboration-Circles.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2024/02/Collaboration-Circles.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2024/02/Collaboration-Circles.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2024/02/Collaboration-Circles.jpg 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/02/Collaboration-Circles.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Join to learn more ğŸ‘‡ </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Reserve Your Spot ğŸ“†</a></div><h1 id=\"see-you-there-%F0%9F%8C%B1\">See you there! ğŸŒ±</h1><p>As we gear up for the ReFi Local Nodes 2024 Kickoff, we stand before the start of an exciting journey. Whether you're a seasoned founder, an enthusiastic newcomer, or simply intrigued by the transformative potential of decentralized collaboration, this gathering promises to be a nexus of inspiration, learning, and communal growth. </p><p>Join us as we unveil the blueprint of a regenerative future and take a collective stride towards a more inclusive, collaborative, and impactful ReFi DAO. Your presence is the key to unlocking this new chapter. Together, let's shape the future of ReFi DAO and forge a legacy of regenerative innovation. See you on February 12th at 4 PM UTC!</p>",
